Get the title for this panel.
@return String title

@return JPanel panel

Initialize the panel as though this is the first time it is

Add a listener to this panel.

Remove the listener from this panel.

String help location for this panel; return null if default help
 location should be used.

methods.comment: Returns the component, if any, that should receive focus when this panel is shown.

the component, if any, that should receive focus when this panel is shown; null
